### 🌍 Global Variables
@host = https://v0ukp6ocy8.execute-api.us-east-1.amazonaws.com/prod
@id = 123456-test              # temporary test ID for PUT/DELETE

### 🚀 1. Create a new Bitcoin position
POST {{host}}/positions
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "symbol": "BTCUSDT",
  "quantity": 0.25,
  "type": "buy",
  "date": "2025-10-12"
}

### 📋 2. Get all positions
GET {{host}}/positions

### 🔍 3. Get position by ID
# 🟡 Replace {{id}} with a real ID from the GET above
GET {{host}}/positions/{{id}}

### ✏️ 4. Update position by ID
PUT {{host}}/positions/{{id}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "symbol": "BTCUSDT",
  "quantity": 0.5,
  "type": "sell",
  "date": "2025-10-13"
}

### ❌ 5. Delete position by ID
DELETE {{host}}/positions/{{id}}

### 🧭 6. Swagger Documentation (UI)
GET {{host}}/docs

### 🏠 7. Frontend (HTML interface)
GET {{host}}/

### 🛠️ 8. Health Check
GET {{host}}/health
